# ModConverter-generated song mods and embedded audio dumps —
# derived from proprietary .xrns / audio sources, treated the
# same as those sources for publication purposes.
Main/Project/src/_BuiltinAssets/
Main/Project/src/BuiltinAssets/Mods/*/
Main/Project/src/Temp/
Tools/ModConverter/.songconverterstate
